h2. Configuration
----------------------------------------------------------------
Configuration files use YAML syntax: http://www.yaml.org/
----------------------------------------------------------------
jyaml.yml				- jyaml configuration
Conf/conf.yaml 			- general configuration
Conf/{aeria|skos}.yaml	- summary model configuration
Conf/summarization.yaml	- output ontology configuration

Conf/OntoIn/*.yaml		- input ontology configuration
Conf/Class/*.yaml		- ontology class configuration
Conf/Prop/*.yaml		- ontology property configuration
================================================================
h2. Output
----------------------------------------------------------------
OntoOut/*
----------------------------------------------------------------
See Conf/summarization.yaml
================================================================


